descriptionHtml:
GPS Navigation:
GPS navigation and maps application has top features like route maker, weather report and GPS compass for android to get directions and GPS speedometer to calculate time, speed and distance. It shows you Map coordinates with latitude longitude for my current location address. Best GPS for car driving directions maps with speaking gives you turn by turn navigation. Also you have satellite map live and topographic map as well as traffic map with traffic info. Road map with location and km with voice navigation.
Route planner:
Walking route planner for walking directions. Cycle route planner with cycle GPS for cycling. Driving route planner for driving and travel route planner for travellers and bike route planner for bikers for biking. It has Map of European countries & map of African countries. Car GPS app is perfect for everyday driving. Truck GPS always find your way and best for truckers to not get lost again. World map 3d having state map, country map and Street maps with 360 street view. Digital speedometer for car & motorcycle GPS speedometer to measure the maximum speed, average speed, distance and time. GPS navigator helps you to arriving at your location safe and sound. Search millions of places and design routes to get there and explore your favorite places and you can save them & share with anyone. Time and distance estimates of multiple routes by walking, cycling, car and bike modes with navigation.
Route Finder:
Find multiple routes on map to your selected location with time and distance. Route tracker to track hiking trails, live traffic, dirt or unpaved trails, bicycle roads & famous places as well as point of interests. Truck route GPS with latest road conditions for truck drivers to get them on their destination easily. This application has useful features like Coordinates finder and address finder to find any place on map. Find east west north south directions by digital compass sensor for android. Maps road and routes. Free detailed maps of entire world with step by step voice navigation. Local weather conditions, directions with compass and as well as accurate altitude according to your location.
Voice GPS Navigation:
Another extraordinary feature of this application is voice GPS navigation. While driving you can’t use hands to type the address so you can use this feature. Ladakh maps and directions. 3d Aerial view maps. Car navigation for car drivers with voice & Truck navigation for truckers with voice. Find location coordinates with lat long that user can copy, share or save. GPS km to measure the distance of your travel. Map hd live Users can enter a destination address then the app automatically calculates directions and distance to the destination.
Weather Updates:
Check weather today through local weather update live feature before starting your journey. Live satellite view of earth with my location map in HD quality. Compass direction to find four cardinal directions by latitude and longitude map. Easy to check temperature outside with the help of live weather related to my location or any other city in the whole world. Voice activated GPS with 3d maps directions guides you with speaking. Earth map 3d online. Best GPS satellite navigation for hikers. Explore tourist attractions and find nearby places.
